sliderContent.text: I always get a friendly, personal reception from both Mary Jane and his staff. When I needed multiple services but had maxed out my insurance, Mary Jane worked with me to identify the worst problem and work out a plan for the rest. Excellent, caring work. I highly recommend Mary Jane and his team.
